msgstr ""
"Der erwartete Dateiname für gültige Firmware-Dateien lautet "
"<b>{filename_pattern}</b>. Für die neuesten offiziellen Firmware-Updates "
"besuche bitte {url}."

#: ../package/FlashGBX/hw_GBxCartRW.py:924
msgid ""
"Please double check that this is a valid firmware file for your GBxCart RW. "
"If it is invalid or an update for a different device, it may render your "
